Novice Panel Missions

■Perform a limit break 3 times on a 5★ affinity weapon (initial CP 15) and enhance it to max
Strategy Tip:
• 5★ affinity weapons are those with an initial rarity of 5★ and an initial CP of 15 that boost an ability of the ally with whom they are associated.
• They can be obtained from draws and by trading in ten power tokens at the power token exchange.
• Power stones can be obtained by selling weapons with an initial rarity of 5★.
　*The power tokens and power stones needed to clear this mission can be obtained by clearing the mission "Clear Act 1, Ch. 1, 'Primus Island.'"
• Refer to the game guide pages below for more information.
